<div id="review_219046651" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/219046651" />
    <a title="Colleen Earle" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5128461-colleen-earle"><img alt="Colleen Earle" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1604833783p2/5128461.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/219046651?book_show_action=true">Oct 04, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Colleen Earle" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Colleen Earle" href="/user/show/5128461-colleen-earle">Colleen Earle</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer219046651" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8962175725258201821">I really enjoy how this book weaves together a historical story and Arthurian legend. <br/>I didn’t remember the plot very well from when I was a child, but I’m excited to read there next in the series which I remember being my favourite.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


